{"title":"CentOS 手动更换内核","uid":"64736f77b89e86715a6b7061bf24c0ba","slug":"2020-11-13-CentOS-手动更换内核","date":"2020-11-13T13:26:07.000Z","updated":"2021-09-26T10:10:40.945Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2020-11-13-CentOS-手动更换内核.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p><img src=\"https://img.zxj.guru/2020/11/centos-upgrade-kernel.png\" alt=\"centos-upgrade-kernel\"></p>\n<p>由于开启 BBR 需 <code>4.10</code> 以上版本 Linux 内核， 但是云服务器安装的 CentOS 7 系统内核是 <code>3.10</code>，低于开启 BBR 最低要求的版本 <code>4.10</code>，所以我们需要手动更换为默认内核后再作升级。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>由于是使用最新版系统内核，最好请勿在生产环境安装，以免产生不可预测之后果。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"安装-ELRepo-yum-源\"><a href=\"#安装-ELRepo-yum-源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 ELRepo yum 源\"></a>安装 ELRepo yum 源</h2><ol>\n<li><p>查看当前 <code>Kernel</code> 版本。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ uname -r\nkernel-3.10.0-1160.11.1.el7.x86_64</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>更新软件包。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">su - root\nyum update -y</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>导入 <code>ELRepo</code> 公钥。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">rpm --import https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.elrepo.org&#x2F;RPM-GPG-KEY-elrepo.org</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>安装 <code>ELRepo</code> 的 yum 源。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#RHEL-8 或者 CentOS-8\nyum install -y https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.elrepo.org&#x2F;elrepo-release-8.el8.elrepo.noarch.rpm\n\n#RHEL-7, SL-7 或者 CentOS-7\nyum install -y https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.elrepo.org&#x2F;elrepo-release-7.el7.elrepo.noarch.rpm\n\n#RHEL-6, SL-6 或者 CentOS-6\nyum install -y https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.elrepo.org&#x2F;elrepo-release-6.el6.elrepo.noarch.rpm</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>安装国内镜像。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#备份 &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;elrepo.repo\ncp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;elrepo.repo &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;elrepo.repo.bak\n\n#安装 TUNA 镜像源\nsed -i &#39;s+mirrorlist&#x3D;+#mirrorlist&#x3D;+&#39; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;elrepo.repo\nsed -i &#39;s+elrepo.org&#x2F;linux+mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;elrepo+&#39; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;yum.repos.d&#x2F;elrepo.repo</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>更新软件包缓存。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum makecache</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"安装新内核\"><a href=\"#安装新内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装新内核\"></a>安装新内核</h2><ol>\n<li><p>查看 <code>ELRepo</code> 仓库下当前系统支持的内核包。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum --disablerepo&#x3D;&quot;*&quot; --enablerepo&#x3D;&quot;elrepo-kernel&quot; list available</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>安装最新的主线稳定<code>Kernel</code> 。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum --enablerepo&#x3D;elrepo-kernel install -y kernel-ml</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"更改-grub-配置默认启动新内核\"><a href=\"#更改-grub-配置默认启动新内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更改 grub 配置默认启动新内核\"></a>更改 grub 配置默认启动新内核</h2><p>安装完<code>kernel-ml</code>之后，系统没有自动切换到新内核，重启之后也不会切换到新内核。我们需要更改 <code>grub</code> 配置默认启动新内核。</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>打开 <code>/etc/default/grub</code> 文件，将文件中<code>GRUB_DEFAULT=saved</code>修改为<code>GRUB_DEFAULT=0</code>。不会 Vim 操作的使用下面命令。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sed -i &#39;s+GRUB_DEFAULT&#x3D;saved+GRUB_DEFAULT&#x3D;0+&#39; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;default&#x2F;grub</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>重新生成 <code>Kernel</code> 配置。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">grub2-mkconfig -o &#x2F;boot&#x2F;grub2&#x2F;grub.cfg</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>重启服务器。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">reboot</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>检查是否更改为新 <code>Kernel</code> 。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ uname -r\n5.10.4-1.el7.elrepo.x86_64</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"删除多余内核\"><a href=\"#删除多余内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除多余内核\"></a>删除多余内核</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>如果空间充裕建议不要卸载旧内核。</p></blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li><p>查看所有版本的 <code>Kernel</code> 。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">rpm -qa | grep kernel</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>删除旧版本的 <code>Kernel</code> 。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo yum remove -y kernel-3.10.*</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>重新生成 <code>Kernel</code> 配置。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo grub2-mkconfig -o &#x2F;boot&#x2F;grub2&#x2F;grub.cfg</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"参考\"><a href=\"#参考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考\"></a>参考</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/elrepo/\">elrepo | 镜像站使用帮助 | 清华大学开源软件镜像站</a></li>\n</ul>\n","text":" 由于开启 BBR 需 4.10 以上版本 Linux 内核， 但是云服务器安装的 CentOS 7 系统内核是 3.10，低于开启 BBR 最低要求的版本 4.10，所以我们需要手动更换为默认内核后再作升级。 由于是使用最新版系统内核，最好请勿在生产环境安装，以免产生不可预测之...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"CentOS","slug":"CentOS","count":5,"path":"api/categories/CentOS.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CentOS","slug":"CentOS","count":5,"path":"api/tags/CentOS.json"},{"name":"Kernel","slug":"Kernel","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Kernel.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-ELRepo-yum-%E6%BA%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装 ELRepo yum 源</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%96%B0%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装新内核</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9-grub-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%96%B0%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">更改 grub 配置默认启动新内核</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BD%99%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除多余内核</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">参考</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"JaimeZeng","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https: